11 (d) For taxable years beginning on or after January 1, 2023, but [prior] to January
12 1, 2024, the tax shall be four and one-half percent (4.5%) of net income.
13 (e) For taxable years beginning on or after January 1, 2024, but before January 1,
14 2026, the tax shall be four percent (4%) of net income.
15 (f) For taxable years beginning on or after January 1, 2026, the tax shall be three
16 and one-half percent (3.5%) of net income.
