22 1. Two percent (2%) of the amount of net income up to three thousand
23 dollars ($3,000);
24 2. Three percent (3%) of the amount of net income over three thousand
25 dollars ($3,000) and up to four thousand dollars ($4,000);
26 3. Four percent (4%) of the amount of net income over four thousand
27 dollars ($4,000) and up to five thousand dollars ($5,000);
